data.description: Marvel at the thought &design put into this one of a kind home on~20 wooded ac. Completely custom all metal exterior w/epitome of rustic charm within. Concrete floors, recalimed wood walls &ceilings, corregated elements, track doors throughout, industrial sink/lighting/fixtures, clawfoot tub, open concept living, cathedral ceiling, wrap around covered porch, XL fenced garden, chick coop w/run &2 large workshops. Fruit trees. Turkey/bear/deer. Loft can easily convert to additional bedrooms. Appliances neg.
